---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../../config/site';

const title = 'Industry references — MT Middle East';
const description = 'A curated selection of specialist media, industry portals and reference bodies for valve and fitting professionals — covering technical guidance, market intelligence and regional construction trends.';
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} lang="en-GB">
  <article class="max-w-editorial mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-20">

    <a href="/articles" class="eyebrow text-steel hover:text-accent transition">&larr; All news</a>

    <div class="mt-6 eyebrow text-accent">Editorial · Resources</div>

    <h1 class="mt-3 font-display font-bold text-4xl lg:text-6xl tracking-tight leading-tight">
      International references worth following: the publications, portals and events that shape our sector
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-graphite max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
      A curated selection of specialist media, industry portals and reference bodies for valve and fitting professionals — covering technical guidance, market intelligence and regional construction trends. Prepared by the MT technical team.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 prose prose-lg max-w-3xl text-graphite leading-relaxed space-y-6">

      <p>
        Staying technically current and commercially informed is part of the job for anyone specifying, distributing or installing valves in today's market. The sector publishes a substantial volume of material every year — technical articles, market reports, normative updates, trade show coverage — and not all of it is equally useful.
      </p>

      <p>
        The selection below has been prepared by the MT technical team based on three criteria: technical relevance, geographic coverage, and practical utility for distributors, MEP specifiers and contractors active in European and GCC markets. It contains no affiliate links. Publications are listed solely for their sectoral reference value.
      </p>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 max-w-4xl overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full text-sm text-left border-collapse">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b-2 border-ink">
            <th class="py-3 pr-4 font-display font-semibold text-ink uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">#</th>
            <th class="py-3 pr-4 font-display font-semibold text-ink uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Publication</th>
            <th class="py-3 pr-4 font-display font-semibold text-ink uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Sector</th>
            <th class="py-3 pr-4 font-display font-semibold text-ink uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Type</th>
            <th class="py-3 font-display font-semibold text-ink uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Why it matters</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="text-graphite">

          <tr class="border-b border-mist">
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top font-mono text-steel">01</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top"><strong class="text-ink">Valve World</strong><br/><span class="text-xs text-steel">valve-world.net</span></td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Valves</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Technical journal</td>
            <td class="py-4 align-top">The international reference publication dedicated exclusively to industrial valves. Engineering articles, product launches, manufacturer interviews and coverage of trade shows including Valve World Expo (Düsseldorf). Essential reading for the sector.</td>
          </tr>

          <tr class="border-b border-mist">
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top font-mono text-steel">02</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top"><strong class="text-ink">Fluid Handling Pro</strong><br/><span class="text-xs text-steel">fluidhandlingpro.com</span></td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Valves · Fluid handling</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Technical portal</td>
            <td class="py-4 align-top">Specialist portal covering valves, pumps, actuators and piping across oil &amp; gas, water, food and pharma sectors. Particularly strong on application-specific technical guides and product selection criteria.</td>
          </tr>

          <tr class="border-b border-mist">
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top font-mono text-steel">03</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top"><strong class="text-ink">Big 5 Global — Knowledge Hub</strong><br/><span class="text-xs text-steel">big5construct.com</span></td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Construction · MENA</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Trade show + content</td>
            <td class="py-4 align-top">The portal of the Middle East's most important construction fair includes market reports, sector trends and project analysis for the GCC. The most reliable data source on the Arab construction market. MT attended the November 2025 edition.</td>
          </tr>

          <tr class="border-b border-mist">
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top font-mono text-steel">04</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top"><strong class="text-ink">ASHRAE Journal</strong><br/><span class="text-xs text-steel">ashrae.org/journal</span></td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">HVAC · Energy</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Technical journal</td>
            <td class="py-4 align-top">Official publication of the American Society of Heating, Refrigerating and Air-Conditioning Engineers. Global reference in HVAC engineering and energy efficiency. Chilled water and district cooling guides are especially relevant for GCC valve specification.</td>
          </tr>

          <tr class="border-b border-mist">
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top font-mono text-steel">05</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top"><strong class="text-ink">Construction Week Middle East</strong><br/><span class="text-xs text-steel">constructionweekonline.com</span></td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Construction · MENA</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Regional magazine</td>
            <td class="py-4 align-top">The weekly reference publication for the Middle East construction sector. Covers active projects, contract awards, company movements and key interviews across UAE, Saudi Arabia and Qatar.</td>
          </tr>

          <tr class="border-b border-mist">
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top font-mono text-steel">06</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top"><strong class="text-ink">Water &amp; Wastewater International</strong><br/><span class="text-xs text-steel">waterworld.com/international</span></td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Water · Infrastructure</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Technical journal</td>
            <td class="py-4 align-top">International publication specialising in water infrastructure: treatment, distribution networks, sanitation and desalination. Covers the most relevant GCC water projects for valve specification in hydraulic applications.</td>
          </tr>

          <tr class="border-b border-mist">
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top font-mono text-steel">07</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top"><strong class="text-ink">Global Water Intelligence</strong><br/><span class="text-xs text-steel">globalwaterintel.com</span></td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Water · Market intelligence</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Reports &amp; data</td>
            <td class="py-4 align-top">Market reports and data on the global water and wastewater industry. Their analysis of the MENA water sector provides essential context for understanding the scale of the market MT is entering with the Dubai hub.</td>
          </tr>

          <tr class="border-b border-mist">
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top font-mono text-steel">08</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top"><strong class="text-ink">IVS — Industrial Valve Summit</strong><br/><span class="text-xs text-steel">industrialvalvesummit.com</span></td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Valves · Industrial</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Trade show</td>
            <td class="py-4 align-top">Biennial fair specialising in industrial valves and actuators, held in Bergamo, Italy. Alongside Valve World Expo, the most important European sector gathering for manufacturers, distributors and specifiers.</td>
          </tr>

          <tr class="border-b border-mist">
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top font-mono text-steel">09</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top"><strong class="text-ink">Plumbing &amp; Mechanical</strong><br/><span class="text-xs text-steel">pmmag.com</span></td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Plumbing · MEP</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Technical magazine</td>
            <td class="py-4 align-top">North American technical publication for MEP engineers and installers. Its valve specification guides and normative articles are a reference for professionals working in markets with American normative influence — including the GCC.</td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top font-mono text-steel">10</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top"><strong class="text-ink">EUROVENT</strong><br/><span class="text-xs text-steel">eurovent.org</span></td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">HVAC · Standards</td>
            <td class="py-4 pr-4 align-top text-xs">Association + publications</td>
            <td class="py-4 align-top">European association of HVAC and refrigeration equipment manufacturers. Product certification publications and energy efficiency market studies are key references for HVAC component specification in Europe and markets adopting European standards.</td>
          </tr>

        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 prose prose-lg max-w-3xl text-graphite leading-relaxed space-y-6">

      <p>
        <strong class="text-ink">Editorial note:</strong> This selection has been prepared by the MT team and is not exhaustive. Other valuable sources include national valve manufacturer associations (CEIR in Europe, VMA in North America), national water utility technical bulletins (DEWA, Kahramaa, SAWS), and the technical libraries of major engineering consultancies active in the GCC. If you work in a specific niche — pharma, food and beverage, oil &amp; gas downstream — your most useful sources may differ. Use this list as a starting point, not as an endpoint.
      </p>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-10 border-t border-mist">
      <div class="eyebrow text-steel">Talk to MT Middle East</div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-lg">
        For technical questions, certificate copies, BIM/CAD files, or to discuss a project specification, talk to our team in Dubai.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-lg">
        <a href={'mailto:' + site.email} class="text-accent underline hover:text-accentDark">{site.email}</a>
        &nbsp;·&nbsp; {site.phone} &nbsp;·&nbsp; {site.hours}
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-6 inline-block bg-ink text-paper px-6 py-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider2 hover:bg-accent transition">
        Contact us &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>

  </article>
</BaseLayout>
